Installing pyspotify 
====================

If you haven't already installed libspotify, you can use the included one by doing this:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$PWD/lib

installation of pyspotify on jaunty for python2.6:
    python setup.py install --install-layout=deb --prefix=/usr/local

however best for now is something like:

sudo python setup.py develop

Try the example1 script with your spotify credentials:

./example1.py -u USERNAME -p PASSWORD

